> This mod adds a raider boss called the Gashslit: 
> orginal Creator: min01 New Creater: magispeller_illagebossmaker,Theillagecoder
- · It has a chance (configurable) to appear during raids;
- · Has 680 (×340) HP and can deal 13~24 damage depending on the attack move;
- · The lower this boss's remaining HP, the higher its defense/attack damage;
- · When HP is 40% or less, it will change phase: unlocking new attack methods and additionally increasing attack damage and range;
- · After performing a melee attack, this boss gains Speed level 10 for a very short time;
- · This boss can also shoot sword energy to attack targets from a distance;
- · Charge attack: quickly rushes toward the target and deals at least 46 damage;
- · Summon: summons several Riftblade King Dragons to assist in battle;
- · Block: during this action, the boss becomes immune to most damage;
- · Slash barrage: this move can deal very high damage in a short time (20 damage/second);
- · This boss currently has no added drops.
